Beware the Batman is an American computer-animated television series based on the DC Comics superhero Batman. The series was premiered in the United States on Cartoon Network on July 13, 2013,[1] as part of their DC Nation block.[2] It is the replacement for Batman: The Brave and the Bold. Beware the Batman is produced by Warner Bros. Animation.[3]
